main event: A student observed an unidentified flying object near Denville, New Jersey on April 7, 1967.
interesting points: The sighting occurred at approximately 7:00 p.m.,The object moved erratically making sudden changes in direction and speed,The report included additional sightings from April to August 1967 but was submitted too late to investigate, The sight was noted to be of a white light with no sound,Observations varied in duration from 1 minute to 15 minutes.
